Title: S3 Ep. 118 The Future of Podcasting
Description: What do you think the future of podcasting will be 5-10 years from now. Do you listen to podcasts? If you're listening to this right now, then you will hear how listening to podcasts may be integrated into our home life but possibly our minds. Tune in to this special episode as we discuss the past, present, and future of podcasting.
